00:15:08.100 --> 00:15:12.260
Yeah, so realbreadoutreach.com is our ministry,

00:15:12.260 --> 00:15:15.540
and we are now, like I said, we built a bakery as well

00:15:15.540 --> 00:15:17.460
in Gonaives, Haiti, and they're feeding

00:15:17.460 --> 00:15:21.140
12 to 1300 school children in the community every day.

00:15:21.140 --> 00:15:24.660
We've reached out, we built a bakery in Tanzania.

00:15:24.660 --> 00:15:27.700
They're feeding, they're making 150 to 200 loaves a day

00:15:27.700 --> 00:15:30.120
feeding the community, and we've started

00:15:30.120 --> 00:15:31.980
a pastors feeding program.

00:15:31.980 --> 00:15:36.780
