If somebody signed up at $25 a month,

00:15:53.140 --> 00:15:54.180
where would the money go?

00:15:54.180 --> 00:15:57.860
It would go straight to one of the pastors in Tanzania.

00:15:57.860 --> 00:16:01.120
It takes $25 a month, it's 10 pounds of rice,

00:16:01.120 --> 00:16:03.140
five pounds of beans, five pounds of corn,

00:16:03.140 --> 00:16:05.260
five pounds of wheat, a liter of oil,

00:16:05.260 --> 00:16:07.660
some sugar and some salt, and they get that every month.

00:16:07.660 --> 00:16:09.500
That could feed a whole village.

00:16:09.500 --> 00:16:11.900
Well, it feeds one person for a whole month.

00:16:11.900 --> 00:16:12.740
Okay, one person.

00:16:12.740 --> 00:16:15.140
Some of the pastors have families,

00:16:15.140 --> 00:16:16.740
so that would just be for him.

00:16:16.740 --> 00:16:19.300
So some, it's $100 for the family,

00:16:19.300 --> 00:16:21.860
and you can go online and see some of the pastors

00:16:21.860 --> 00:16:24.370
and their families and how many people are in that

00:16:24.370 --> 00:16:24.940
family.

00:16:24.940 --> 00:16:27.440
So you could sponsor a family if you wanted to,

00:16:27.440 --> 00:16:30.860
but the main thing I just want people to know is

00:16:30.860 --> 00:16:35.100
the ministry is self-funded, or, well, it's not self-funded,

00:16:35.100 --> 00:16:37.820
it's funded, there's no paid employees,

00:16:37.820 --> 00:16:40.220
